# handoff

Full workflow: `.claude/skills/handoff/SKILL.md`.

Fill `docs/prompts/template.md`'s ROLE/PROJECT CONTEXT/OBJECTIVE/REQUIREMENTS/CONSTRAINTS/OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS/SAVE OUTPUT AS shape — ROLE comes from CLAUDE.md's AI Collaboration Model (ChatGPT = PM/Architect, Gemini = Research Analyst, Claude = Senior Engineer). Include decisions already made and why; exclude anything already permanently recorded in `/docs` (link instead of repeating). Save the filled template as `docs/prompts/<date>-<slug>.md`.
